克或血液中酒精濃度\r\n    達百分之零點零五以上。","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/CHDM/111%2c%e4%ba%a4%e7%b0%a1%2c1973%2c20221013%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"CHDM,111,交簡,1973,20221013,1","JYEAR":"111","JCASE":"交簡","JNO":"1973","JDATE":"20221013","JTITLE":"公共危險"}